snippet.title: Clevver News
snippet.description:
Clevver is THE #1 source for pop culture, entertainment, and celebrity news, interviews, and more! 

Welcome to Clevver News! Clevver News is your one stop shop for all things pop culture, entertainment, celebrity news, gossip, TEA & much more! We've got a variety of shows that will fulfill anyone's entertainment craving such as Newsfeed, Listed, Daily Hollywood Rundown & more. Come join in on the fun and get INFOtained!  
 
We want to make Clevver News a safe place for our hosts and our audience. Your comments are always welcome, even if they are critiques. However, we will delete your remarks if they are deemed off-topic, contain vulgar language, or are disrespectful of others.
